{"id":8216,"date":"2026-03-20T15:59:08","date_gmt":"2026-03-20T08:59:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8216"},"modified":"2026-03-20T15:59:08","modified_gmt":"2026-03-20T08:59:08","slug":"octinoxate-mang-loc-uvb","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/octinoxate-mang-loc-uvb\/","title":{"rendered":"Octinoxate \u2013 M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc UVB quen thu\u1ed9c trong kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Octinoxate, l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1eb7n tia UVB \u2013 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh g\u00e2y b\u1ecfng n\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng DNA b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u0169ng v\u00ec l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00e2u, Octinoxate l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem x\u00e9t k\u1ef9 h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 t\u00ednh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh quang h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-quan-ve-mang-loc-octinoxate\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng quan v\u1ec1 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Octinoxate<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc\/INCI: Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate (c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Octinoxate, Octyl Methoxycinnamate).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u00f3m: M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc (UV filter) \u2013 thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m cinnamate.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vai tr\u00f2: H\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 tia UVB (280\u2013320 nm), ng\u0103n ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng DNA b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c: \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c FDA ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng n\u0103m 1980; v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u khu v\u1ef1c (EU, Nh\u1eadt, \u00dac) nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00ean th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn: Parsol MCX, Eusolex 2292, Uvinul MC 80.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8218 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-2.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ed5 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u1ee7a octinoxate trong v\u00f9ng 288-320nm\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-mang-loc-octinoxate\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Octinoxate<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 tia UVB m\u1ea1nh: gi\u00fap t\u0103ng SPF cho kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng, b\u1ecfng r\u00e1t v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng DNA b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p: Octinoxate th\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc UVA (Avobenzone, Uvinul A Plus, Tinosorb S) \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ph\u1ed5 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c: kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec7t tr\u1eafng, cho c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9 \u2013 d\u1ec5 t\u00e1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh th\u1ea5p \u2013 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh khi s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p: d\u1ec5 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi trong c\u1ea3 kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, kem n\u1ec1n, d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da ban ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Octinoxate h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1eeb tia UVB, sau \u0111\u00f3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7t nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t t\u00e1n v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i ra m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u1eefu c\u01a1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Octinoxate d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n h\u1ee7y d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi (k\u00e9m b\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng), \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i k\u00e8m (nh\u01b0 Tinosorb S, Uvinul A Plus, Octocrylene). Khi b\u1ecb ph\u00e2n h\u1ee7y, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 gi\u1ea3m v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ecf g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-su-dung-octinoxate\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Octinoxate<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-kcn-co-ethylhexyl-methoxycinnamate-octinoxate-dung-tot-nhat-khi-nao\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng KCN c\u00f3 Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate (Octinoxate) d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi n\u00e0o?<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sinh ho\u1ea1t h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y: ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p trong kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ban ng\u00e0y, make-up, kem n\u1ec1n, BB\/CC cream c\u00f3 ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u2013 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong nh\u00e0: Octinoxate cho l\u1edbp n\u1ec1n m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng, kh\u00f4ng v\u1ec7t tr\u1eafng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01a1n l\u1ebb khi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac n\u1eafng m\u1ea1nh: v\u00ec kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng k\u00e9m b\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc (Avobenzone, Tinosorb S, Uvinul A Plus\u2026).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><b>C\u00f3 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh ho\u1eb7c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Octinoxate?<\/b><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8220\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8220\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8220 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-4.webp\" alt=\"Octinoxate c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9c san h\u00f4 \" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8220\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Octinoxate c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9c san h\u00f4<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u00e9m b\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng: d\u1ec5 gi\u1ea3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh quang.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng nh\u1eb9: r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p \u1edf da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c quanh m\u1eaft.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng: m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u cho th\u1ea5y Octinoxate c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn san h\u00f4 v\u00e0 sinh v\u1eadt bi\u1ec3n, n\u00ean b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m trong KCN d\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Hawaii v\u00e0 Palau.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01a1n l\u1ebb trong s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c tr\u1ebb em.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phu-nu-co-thai-va-cho-con-bu-co-dung-duoc-khong\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng?<img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8219 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-3.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/Octinoxate-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng. Octinoxate \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FDA cho ph\u00e9p trong gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 (t\u1ed1i \u0111a 7,5% t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9, 10% t\u1ea1i EU), nh\u01b0ng thi\u1ebfu d\u1eef li\u1ec7u d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1ec1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft \u1edf ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi nh\u00f3m thai k\u1ef3 ho\u1eb7c cho con b\u00fa, n\u00ean \u01b0u ti\u00ean kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng kho\u00e1ng (Zinc Oxide, Titanium Dioxide) an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n v\u00e0 tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn b\u00e1c s\u0129 khi d\u00f9ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-bao-che-phoi-hop-thuong-gap-cua-octinoxate\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng b\u00e0o ch\u1ebf &amp; ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p c\u1ee7a Octinoxate<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>D\u1ea1ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> kem, lotion, s\u1eefa ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, kem n\u1ec1n, cushion, BB cream.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh quang h\u1ecdc:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Octinoxate + Tinosorb S: ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng, b\u1ec1n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Octinoxate + Uvinul A Plus: b\u1ed5 sung UVA1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Octinoxate + Octocrylene: t\u0103ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh quang h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Octinoxate + ZnO\/TiO\u2082 (hybrid): b\u1ec1n h\u01a1n, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea3 UVA\/UVB.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/su-kien\/tinosorb-s-mang-loc-chong-nang-pho-rong\/\">M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Tinosorb S\u00a0<\/a><\/p>\n<p><b>V\u00ec sao m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 h\u00e3ng ng\u1eebng d\u00f9ng Octinoxate?<\/b><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Do t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u1ec3n v\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ty chuy\u1ec3n sang m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi (Tinosorb S, Uvinul A Plus, Methylene Bis-Benzotriazolyl Tetramethylbutylphenol\u2026).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Octinoxate c\u00f3 ch\u1ed1ng UVA kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><b><br \/>\n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng. Octinoxate ch\u1ec9 ch\u1eb7n UVB, n\u00ean c\u1ea7n ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc UVA1\/UVA2 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng (PA\/PPD cao).<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">Ataman Chemicals. (n.d.). <em>Ethylhexyl methoxycinnamate (Octinoxate)<\/em>. <a class=\"underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current\/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current\" href=\"https:\/\/www.atamanchemicals.com\/ethylhexyl-methoxycinnamate_u32149\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/www.atamanchemicals.com\/ethylhexyl-methoxycinnamate_u32149\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">Campaign for Safe Cosmetics. (2022, July 7). <em>Octinoxate<\/em>. <a class=\"underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current\/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current\" href=\"https:\/\/www.safecosmetics.org\/chemicals\/octinoxate\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/www.safecosmetics.org\/chemicals\/octinoxate\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p class=\"font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]\">Environmental Working Group. (n.d.). <em>The trouble with sunscreen chemicals<\/em>. EWG&#8217;s Guide to Sunscreens. <a class=\"underline underline underline-offset-2 decoration-1 decoration-current\/40 hover:decoration-current focus:decoration-current\" href=\"https:\/\/www.ewg.org\/sunscreen\/report\/the-trouble-with-sunscreen-chemicals\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/www.ewg.org\/sunscreen\/report\/the-trouble-with-sunscreen-chemicals\/<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate (Octinoxate) \u2013 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc UVB ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn, gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi ch\u00e1y n\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u00e3o h\u00f3a s\u1edbm do tia UVB<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8217,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8216","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-su-kien"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8216","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8216"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8216\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9291,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8216\/revisions\/9291"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8217"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8216"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=8216"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/